children.name: nature
children.description: Beautiful 3D plants, rocks, and trees to fill your Blender scenes.

name: HDR
description: HDRs let you illuminate your scenes with a single click from our add-on.

children.name: Studio
children.description: Make studio renders of your 3D models in under 1 minute with these HDRs

name: material
description: Did you know? BlenderKit hosts the largest 100% free library of Blender 3D materials.

children.name: Commercial
children.description: Can a shop be any cuter? Maybe just in the case of a toy house or a metal swing.

children.name: Historic
children.description: Discover historical architectural exteriors. A castle missing in your scene? Or maybe the Eiffel tower? Enrich your 3D Environments by mixing past and present.

children.name: Other
children.description: Sometimes a lighthouse or a wind turbine is all you really need for a great 3D render.

children.name: Private
children.description: Find your dream home, apartment building, skyscraper or cottage. In the inflation age, real estate is everything.

children.name: Sci-fi
children.description: There is no limit to Sci-fi architecture. Create realities out of fantasies.

children.name: Door
children.description: Our 3D door collection is amazing. Find the perfect door for the perfect model. Door handles are no exception.

children.name: Bench
children.description: A wooden bench, a plastic bench, and even one made of stone. Just come and sit on it.  Great for public space 3D archviz work or for your 3D movie hero to sit down on and read some newspaper.

children.name: Facade element
children.description: Facade elements in all shapes and forms. Add some cool graffiti to your 3D city.

children.name: Fence
children.description: Divide gardens, parks, lands and nationalities with beautiful textured metal, wood and plastic 3D fence models. The sky is the limit. Or is it?

children.name: Fountain
children.description: Wall fountains and garden geysers are ideal for 3D landscaping and your public space ArchViz scenes

children.name: Other
children.description: What about a 3D garden sculpture? Or a 3d model of a  ventilation pipe? Add some weird and inspiring details to your architectural dreams.

children.name: Playground
children.description: Nobody likes to swing alone. Add some slides and a toy house to your playground. And yes, your ArchViz clients probably do have kids.

children.name: Swimming pool
children.description: Everything looks cooler when your client knows he can swim after his morning coffee. Give your ArchViz scenes that cool look. Or do you need a 3D swimming pool in a blockbuster movie?

children.name: Urban Environment
children.description: Everything from an ancient Greek tower to a modern garbage can. Make 3D city design great again.

children.name: 3D Panel
children.description: Decorate historical or contemporary buildings with ornaments and carvings. Give your 3D scenes a touch of luxury

children.name: Decoration
children.description: Interior decorations to fill your 3D scenes with every possible detail

children.name: Interior
children.description: Architectural Visualization with Blender made easy. Fill your scenes in minutes instead of hours.

name: Scene
description: BlenderKit scenes help you finish your projects faster. Use finished scenes and tweak them, or use templates and fill them with your designs.
